[I] The Cinnamon session manager

[T] cinnamon-session is the session manager for the Cinnamon Desktop. It starts
[T] up the desktop environment, loads saved sessions or provides a default
[T] session for the user.

[U] https://github.com/linuxmint/cinnamon-session

